Interface BasicResourceInitializer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBasicHandler, BasicButtonHandler, BasicDropDownButtonHandler, BasicHandler, BasicMenuHandler, BasicSelectableHandler, BasicSelectableHandler.Check, BasicSelectableHandler.Radio

    public interface BasicResourceInitializer
    A BasicResourceInitializer is a helper class used by a BasicButtonModel to lazily initialize resources.

    Benjamin Sigg
